{
  "stem": "56.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we used to-- we learned to make cake out of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did we make cake?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used the barley and a piece of bread to keep it together, and saccharin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we used to make a cake out of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we found so many things we could do with so many-- so that was one of the things we ate.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But whatever we could find.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were always hungry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Always.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was never a day in the ghetto that I wasn't hungry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We found out that-- when we planted things, we couldn't wait till it grew, so we used to eat the leaves that came up, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before something develops in the ground, there are leaves, so we used to pick the leaves and eat them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was-- the rations we got were just almost nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A piece of bread and a watery soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How can you survive on that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, you-- either you suffer from malnutrition, or you just find other things to eat that you can get something from.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just-- whatever was edible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think if-- if-- if there were any rats or mice in the ghetto, we would have eaten them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But unfortunately, there weren't any, because there was no food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We tried to catch birds, but after a while, there were no birds.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It never dawned on me till after the war, to-- one day when I heard the birds singing, I said, my god, there were no birds in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I remember why.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No animal would go where there was no food.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
